ón delirium multicomponente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"76","text":"Evaluación nutricional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"76","text":"Revisión farmacológica\\N(STOPP/START)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"76","text":"Planificación alta y\\Ncontinuidad de cuidados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"76","text":"Prevención secundaria osteoporosis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"69","text":"Estudio Middleton 2017 (Age Ageing)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Cambio de GCS → ICM integrado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"n=1.894 pacientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"↓ estancia 27.5 → **21\\Ndías** (p<0.001)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"↓ tiempo a cirugía 41.8 →\\N**27.2h** (p<0.001)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"↓ mortalidad 30d 13.2% →\\N**10.3%** (p=0.04)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"85","text":"OR mortalidad ajustado\\N**0.68** (p=0.03)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"0","text":"Comparación Resumida de Modelos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Indicador → GCS < GW ≈ ICM","guid":"","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"Mortalidad intrahospitalaria →\\Ntodos ↓ vs cuidado usual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"Estancia hospitalaria → **ICM\\Nmayor reducción** (SMD -0.61)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"94","text":"Tiempo a cirugía → sin diferencia\\Nsignificativa entre modelos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"94","text":"Readmisión 30 días →\\Nsin efecto claro","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"94","text":"Outcomes funcionales →\\Ninconsistente en todos los modelos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"93","text":"Costo-efectividad","guid":"","children":[{"